The paper deals with the problem of detecting malicious URLs using machine learning techniques. This problem falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also uses bagging algorithms, which are commonly used in machine learning (cs.AI). The use of machine learning for classification also falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). The paper deals with the problem of text classification, which is a subfield of information retrieval (cs.IR). Finally, the paper discusses the deployment of the model in a real-time system, which falls under the category of software engineering (cs.SE).
